Female 
<emphasis id="15CC115DFFBCFF92FD39F8FCFD0AF8CB" bold="true" box="[675,700,1864,1888]" pageId="4" pageNumber="487">A.</emphasis>
Body in frontal view. 
<emphasis id="15CC115DFFBCFF92FC3FF8FCFC0BF8CB" bold="true" box="[933,957,1864,1888]" pageId="4" pageNumber="487">B.</emphasis>
Head and inner side of fore leg. 
<emphasis id="15CC115DFFBCFF92FA88F8FCFA9DF8CB" bold="true" box="[1298,1323,1864,1888]" pageId="4" pageNumber="487">C.</emphasis>
Outer side of fore leg. 
<emphasis id="15CC115DFFBCFF92FE97F8D8FE90F82F" bold="true" box="[269,294,1900,1924]" pageId="4" pageNumber="487">D.</emphasis>
Tegmina.
</paragraph>
