<paragraph id="2707CD4FFFBDFF93FF5DFF0EFE44FF52" blockId="5.[151,1437,150,429]" pageId="5" pageNumber="488">
<emphasis id="15CC115DFFBDFF93FF5DFF0EFE52FF7F" bold="true" box="[199,484,186,212]" pageId="5" pageNumber="488">Measurements (in mm).</emphasis>
Tl: 24–29, Ol: 0.20–0.21, Id: 0.30–0.32, Ood: 0.12–0.15, Pl: 4–7, Pw 4.5–6: Pf: 0.9, Teg: 8–9, Hf: 4.5–5, Ht: 3–3.5.
